query:
SELECT 
  s.id as session_id,
  COUNT(m.id) as message_count,
  s.plantProfile,
  DATE_FORMAT(s.createdAt, '%Y-%m-%d') as created_date
FROM sessions s
LEFT JOIN messages m ON s.id = m.sessionId
GROUP BY s.id
ORDER BY message_count DESC, s.id DESC
LIMIT 20;
